st-hong-kong-artists-where-to-find-them/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3666401-14338735334823aa063632460a8154915630c3f9cc.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/asia/hong-kong/articles/the-10-best-hong-kong-artists-where-to-find-them/"><h3>The 10 Best Hong Kong Artists &amp; Where To Find Them</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">With its own art scene flourishing in recent years, here is a list of the top Hong Kong artists and where you can find their innovative works.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1429217941"><a href="/north-america/articles/top-9-street-artists-from-around-the-world/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3640201-142884813948681bd68252421f83593d9d066ed587.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/north-america/articles/top-9-street-artists-from-around-the-world/"><h3>Top 9 Street Artists From Around The World</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Street art has become a recognized and respected form of art over the past ten years.  A subversive medium, street art is often social and political, yet vibrant and dynamic. Here is a list of the top 9 street artists that will blow your mind.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1429031048"><a href="/africa/articles/the-top-12-artists-you-need-to-follow-on-instagram-/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3639007-142843971154db2108baba4107b7d8bc918056220b.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/africa/articles/the-top-12-artists-you-need-to-follow-on-instagram-/"><h3>The Top 12 Artists You Need To Follow On Instagram </h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">From cutting-edge street graffitists in South Af