					<div class="panel panel-presentation presentation"><h2>Beijing Culture Guide</h2><ul class="presentation-tabs"><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li></ul><div class="panel-content"><a href="#" class="left presentation-nav"></a><a href="#" class="right presentation-nav"></a><div class="presentation-container" data-auto="NO"><div class="presentation-slide"><a href="/asia/china/articles/beijing-cultural-calendar-10-unmissable-spring-events/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-258946-56-246507-beijing-the-forbidden-city-by-james-norman.jpg);"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade"><a href="/asia/china/articles/beijing-cultural-calendar-10-unmissable-spring-events/"><h3>Beijing Cultural Calendar</h3><ul class="breadcrumb"><li>China</li><li class="category">travel</li></ul></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text"><p>See what’s on in Beijing this spring with our guide to ten of the best art, food and culture events taking from April to June.</p></div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide"><a href="/asia/china/articles/beijing-s-top-10-events-this-summer-art-food-and-festivals/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-257149-cover.jpg);"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/asia/china/articles/beijing-s-top-10-events-this-summer-art-food-and-festivals/"><h3> Beijing's Top 10 Events this Summer</h3><ul class="breadcrumb"><li>China</li><li class="category">travel</li></ul></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text"><p>Explore a varied summer of culture in Beijing, China’s cultural capital.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-presentation presentation"><h2>Shanghai Culture Guide</h2><ul class="presentation-tabs"><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li></ul><div class="panel-co