					<div class="panel panel-presentation presentation"><h2>China Literature</h2><ul class="presentation-tabs"><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li></ul><div class="panel-content"><a href="#" class="left presentation-nav"></a><a href="#" class="right presentation-nav"></a><div class="presentation-container"><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1438074883"><a href="/asia/china/articles/the-best-independent-bookshops-in-shanghai/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3718057-4463973719-a4febd188c-o.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade"><a href="/asia/china/articles/the-best-independent-bookshops-in-shanghai/"><h3>The Best Independent Bookshops in Shanghai</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">We profile the top bookshops in Shanghai, and discover the best specialist and independent bookstores, all with a leisurely literary atmosphere.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1420715296"><a href="/asia/articles/10-award-winning-books-by-asian-authors-you-should-read/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-622459-e-book.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/asia/articles/10-award-winning-books-by-asian-authors-you-should-read/"><h3>10 Award-Winning Books by Asian Authors You Should Read</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Asian authors have had a spectacular year – we check out ten award-winning books produced by writers of Asian origin.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1407336954"><a href="/asia/hong-kong/articles/eileen-chang-s-10-must-read-stories-the-voice-of-hong-kong/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-265981-hong-kong.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/asia/hong-kong/articles/eileen-chang-s-10-must-read-stories-the-voice-of-hong-kong/"><h3>Eileen Chang’s 10 Must-Read Stories | The Voice of Hong Kong</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Discover Shanghai writer Eileen Chang, who captured Hong Kong during wartime and took a groundbreaking stance on women, love and desire.
</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1383055183"><a href="/asia/china/articles/an-interview-with-xiaolu-guo-writer-filmmaker-and-cultural-iconoclast-/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-258726-56-223218-headshot-guo-xiaolu.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/asia/china/articles/an-interview-with-xiaolu-guo-writer-filmmaker-and-cultural-iconoclast-/"><h3>An Interview with Xiaolu Guo: Writer, Filmmaker and Cultural Iconoclast </h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">An interview with writer, filmmaker Xiaolu Guo, exploring national identity, cultural exchange and the concept of home.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1382096940"><a href="/asia/china/articles/the-canonical-works-the-four-classic-novels-of-chinese-literature/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-258730-56-221925-china-novels-1.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/asia/china/articles/the-canonical-works-the-four-classic-novels-of-chinese-literature/"><h3>The Four Classic Novels of Chinese Literature</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Water Margin, Journey to the West, Romance of the Three Kingdoms and Dream of the Red Chamber; these four novels form the core of Chinese classical literature.</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-presentation presentation"><h2>China Cinema</h2><ul class="presentation-tabs"></ul><div class="panel-content"><div class="presentation-container" data-auto="no"><div class="presentation-slide"><a href="/asia/china/articles/zhang-yimou-choreographing-chinese-cinema/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-258749-2004-house-of-flying-daggers-020-1-.jpg);"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade"><a href="/asia/china/articles/zhang-yimou-choreographing-chinese-cinema/"><h3>Zhang Yimou: Chinese Cinema</h3><ul class="breadcrumb"><li>China</li><li class="category">film</li></ul></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text"><p>Zhang Yimou is one of China's most celebrated film directors who has garnered praise both in China and abroad.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-presentation presentation"><h2>China Music</h2><ul class="presentation-tabs"><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li><li class="presentation-tab"></li></ul><div class="panel-content"><a href="#" class="left presentation-nav"></a><a href="#" class="right presentation-nav"></a><div class="presentation-container"><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1442140979"><a href="/asia/china/articles/a-beginner-s-guide-to-beijing-s-unique-peking-opera/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3948943-1441963279e6d116138d814b938c3d1a4ac9b1a790.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade"><a href="/asia/china/articles/a-beginner-s-guide-to-beijing-s-unique-peking-opera/"><h3>A Beginner's Guide To Beijing's Unique Peking Opera</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">A quick guide to surviving your first Peking opera in China.</div></div></div><div class="presentation-slide" data-unix="1440663315"><a href="/asia/china/articles/china-s-metal-music-scene/"><div class="image" style="background-image: url(http://static.theculturetrip.com/images/56-3935160-1440661936bcaa9b85647340dd86092dce88f63970.jpg)"></div></a><div class="presentation-fade" style="opacity:0;"><a href="/asia/china/articles/china-s-metal-music-scene/"><h3>China's Heavy Metal Music Scene</h3></a><div class="clear"></div><div class="presentation-text">Everything you never knew about China's little-known love affair with heavy metal. </div></div></div><div class